                        <p>“My parents were immigrants and I strongly believe in the positive impact immigration has on an economy,” Boulding said.</p>
<p>Because of his personal connection and insight into the probable ramifications for the business world, Boulding has made it his mission to advocate for international students to be able to access business education in the country of their choice.</p>
<p>“I’m a big believer in the power of business to transform the world for the better, but to do so requires developing leaders who will use business as a force for good,” the dean said.</p>

